1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,580
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:38,060
Episode 12

3
00:01:39,259 --> 00:01:40,500
Leader. Leader.

4
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,620
Today the actor

5
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:42,820
for the role Zhao Feiyan will be selected.

6
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:43,660
We are all

7
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:44,979
looking forward to it.

8
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:55,580
It’s the new rule of Shuiyun Theater.

9
00:01:56,140 --> 00:01:58,660
Whether newbies or veterans,

10
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,020
all of you compete on the stage.

11
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,860
Seniority doesn’t matter.

12
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:07,780
Do you memorize the lines of your roles

13
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,940
assigned before?

14
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:09,820
Who will be the first?

15
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:11,140
-Me!
-Me!

16
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,380
Silence! Silence!

17
00:02:13,380 --> 00:02:15,340
Keep in line based on the style of your roles.

18
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:17,140
OK. OK.

19
00:02:22,180 --> 00:02:23,980
Dasheng. You go first.

20
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:25,180
Leader.

21
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:27,260
I’ve been in Shuiyun Theater for many years.

22
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:29,620
I won’t take advantage of my seniority.

23
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:31,860
I’m willing to give this chance to these kids.

24
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:32,700
Cut it out.

25
00:02:33,380 --> 00:02:34,380
Perform right now.

26
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,900
Mr. Du. Please.

27
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:40,420
Sure.

28
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:44,100
Take it.

29
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:48,500
Mr. Du.

30
00:02:56,460 --> 00:03:03,380
♫ I’m Heaven Happiness Star ♫

31
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,860
Speak.

32
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,460
Speak.

33
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:13,940
You feel relieved?

34
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:19,500
The newspaper says that

35
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:22,300
Shang Xirui successfully

36
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:25,780
gain a foothold in Peking again.

37
00:03:28,420 --> 00:03:30,060
I didn’t know until you tell me.

38
00:03:31,220 --> 00:03:32,500
Isn’t it a good thing?

39
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:34,500
Save it.

40
00:03:35,300 --> 00:03:37,780
You didn’t even play with the bird these days.

41
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,060
This bird

42
00:03:39,060 --> 00:03:41,700
twittered lonely all day long.

43
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,579
No one answered back.

44
00:03:44,220 --> 00:03:45,180
I think

45
00:03:45,780 --> 00:03:48,460
if Mr. Cheng hadn’t come forward,

46
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,660
you would have gone to Jiang Rongshou

47
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:52,940
and reasoned with him.

48
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:55,020
No.

49
00:03:56,140 --> 00:03:57,940
I can’t manage all the things.

50
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:01,900
They have their own fates.

51
00:04:02,380 --> 00:04:05,500
He is capable if he can be popular

52
00:04:07,380 --> 00:04:09,140
in the opera circle of Peking.

53
00:04:11,060 --> 00:04:12,660
It depends on his capability

54
00:04:14,260 --> 00:04:17,420
if he can stand on his own feet.

55
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:23,020
Jiang called his nephew back

56
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:25,580
in a hurry.

57
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:29,020
I don’t think he will keep him

58
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:32,020
for massage.

59
00:04:33,900 --> 00:04:36,020
Now I know why you sent men out

60
00:04:36,020 --> 00:04:36,620
three times

61
00:04:36,620 --> 00:04:37,580
a day.

62
00:04:38,420 --> 00:04:40,820
You get information faster than the war report.

63
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,300
Although

64
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:45,100
you don’t speak it out,

65
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:47,820
you are caring about it.

66
00:04:49,420 --> 00:04:51,780
You taught Shang Xirui operas for three years.

67
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:54,380
He wanted to be your apprentice,

68
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,780
but you didn’t meet him anymore.

69
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,780
How could you...

70
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:06,060
♫ I’m Heaven Happiness Star ♫

71
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:10,340
Speak.

72
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:15,060
You can’t. Let me.

73
00:05:16,540 --> 00:05:19,660
♫ Pick and shake ♫

74
00:05:19,900 --> 00:05:23,420
♫ Clip and swing ♫

75
00:05:23,420 --> 00:05:30,860
♫ Swing, godmother ♫

76
00:05:30,860 --> 00:05:32,460
Godmother! Godmother!

77
00:05:33,620 --> 00:05:34,659
How is it?

78
00:05:35,860 --> 00:05:37,260
Not good.

79
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:41,260
It’s a dirty word.

80
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:43,380
You...

81
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,500
You... You have no idea.

82
00:05:48,580 --> 00:05:51,180
Godmother. Godmother.

83
00:05:51,580 --> 00:05:52,620
Eryuehong.

84
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:56,420
Sanyuehong.

85
00:05:58,980 --> 00:05:59,980
Luo Xiangqiu.

86
00:05:59,980 --> 00:06:00,860
Thank you, sir.

87
00:06:02,580 --> 00:06:04,300
Shijiu. Ronglan. Xiuzhi.

88
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:04,740
Go.

89
00:06:04,740 --> 00:06:05,300
Don’t move. Don’t move.

90
00:06:05,300 --> 00:06:06,660
Go back. Go back.

91
00:06:06,660 --> 00:06:07,300
What’s wrong?

92
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:10,300
Don’t go to stage this time.

93
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:11,860
Give the chance

94
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:13,500
to Siyue, Jiuyue, Shiyue.

95
00:06:13,580 --> 00:06:15,740
Let them practice on the stage by acting maids.

96
00:06:16,060 --> 00:06:16,820
Thank you, leader.

97
00:06:16,820 --> 00:06:17,980
Thank you, guys.

98
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,540
Thank you, guys.

99
00:06:20,220 --> 00:06:20,900
Great.

100
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:21,580
Work harder.

101
00:06:27,780 --> 00:06:29,180
Dasheng.

102
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,540
Your performance was terrible.

103
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:36,780
Leader.

104
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:38,180
I play martial roles.

105
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,980
You know I am bad at singing.

106
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:41,500
I will piss off

107
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:42,980
and go to do somersaults. Alright?

108
00:06:43,380 --> 00:06:45,140
Do somersaults and get lost.

109
00:06:45,140 --> 00:06:45,860
Yes, Your Highness.

110
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:51,300
He is good.

111
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:05,420
Good boy.

112
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,460
Doesn’t it still hurt?

113
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:10,060
I can bear it.

114
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:12,380
Good job.

115
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:16,180
You deserve the role.

116
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:18,460
Mr. Du.

117
00:07:19,380 --> 00:07:20,260
What do you think?

118
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,820
Impressive.

119
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:29,340
He is young, and should practice more on stage.

120
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,980
He has injuries

121
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:32,980
but still does well.

122
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:35,900
His martial arts are like yours.

123
00:07:36,420 --> 00:07:37,820
You’re flattering me, Young Master.

124
00:07:38,780 --> 00:07:40,420
I’m far worse than the leader.

125
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:41,740
Stop flattering.

126
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:43,060
Practice harder.

127
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:43,700
Leader.

128
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:46,980
La Yuehong is the leading role. What about me?

129
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:49,180
We have a role of the general.

130
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,820
That is a supporting role.

131
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,940
You want me to support La Yuehong?

132
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,540
Don't get mad.

133
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,820
We have

134
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,180
new rules.

135
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:58,820
Who performs better, who goes to the stage.

136
00:07:58,820 --> 00:07:59,820
Leader.

137
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:02,940
You mean my performance isn't good. Right?

138
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:08,580
How hard you work,

139
00:08:09,580 --> 00:08:11,140
how capable you will be.

140
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:14,100
Acting skills regress without practice.

141
00:08:14,220 --> 00:08:15,980
Your leader has said just know.

142
00:08:16,100 --> 00:08:17,940
Good performance matters,

143
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,700
regardless of your age.

144
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:22,300
Many old men are still support actors.

145
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,660
Mr. Du.

146
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:26,260
As a professor, are you lecturing here?

147
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:27,140
Fine.

148
00:08:27,660 --> 00:08:28,980
My skills are inferior.

149
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,500
I deserve to

150
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:32,900
give way to the young generation.

151
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:35,460
I treat you morning tea.

152
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:38,220
Come with me, buddies.

153
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:40,820
Morning tea? Great.

154
00:08:41,059 --> 00:08:42,860
I know a good restaurant.

155
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:43,940
Lamb stuffing.

156
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,060
It’s tasty.

157
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,660
Let’s go to

158
00:08:45,980 --> 00:08:46,740
have some tea.

159
00:08:46,740 --> 00:08:47,540
Let’s go.

160
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,140
Don’t go to school. I don't agree.

161
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:52,340
I am in charge of this family.

162
00:08:52,660 --> 00:08:53,900
The kids of other families can go to school.

163
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,740
Why can't I?

164
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:57,340
I don’t care.

165
00:08:57,340 --> 00:08:58,300
I will go to school.

166
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,260
If your tutor isn’t knowledgeable,

167
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:02,100
I can hire another one

168
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:02,740
for you.

169
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,260
If you go out

170
00:09:04,260 --> 00:09:05,300
and something bad happens to you,

171
00:09:05,300 --> 00:09:06,980
I will feel sorry to your ancestors.

172
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:10,220
Does it have anything to do with our ancestors?

173
00:09:12,340 --> 00:09:13,780
He doesn’t go home at night.

174
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,180
You want to go out.

175
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:17,260
Do you want this family or not?

176
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:20,100
How come I don’t want this family?

177
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:22,060
Go away.

178
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:08,540
Did you argue with her?

179
00:10:15,780 --> 00:10:17,180
Chacha’er

180
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:20,220
is 14 years old this year. Right?

181
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,020
Let me tell you.

182
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,900
In terms of some new ideas,

183
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:43,540
You can’t reason with her at all.

184
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:45,940
Since you can’t,

185
00:10:46,420 --> 00:10:47,380
don’t reason with her.

186
00:10:47,780 --> 00:10:49,020
Or else, she’ll be mad.

187
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:56,420
I don’t agree with her

188
00:10:56,980 --> 00:10:58,420
on her old-fashioned ideas either.

189
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:00,540
Times change.

190
00:11:00,820 --> 00:11:01,580
Right?

191
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,620
If girls don't get any education

192
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:05,540
and horizon is limited,

193
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:06,940
they will be

194
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:09,940
manipulated by husband when married.

195
00:11:10,900 --> 00:11:13,100
They cannot educate children properly either.

196
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:14,100
Am I right?

197
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,260
But

198
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:21,940
I don’t argue with her, do I?

199
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:25,100
I never argue with her.

200
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,180
In that case,

201
00:11:28,740 --> 00:11:30,260
you sacrifice me?

202
00:11:31,060 --> 00:11:32,540
I mean,

203
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:36,020
don’t argue with her face to face.

204
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,060
We can do it gradually behind her.

205
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:49,580
Chacha’er.

206
00:11:50,740 --> 00:11:52,900
I remember you were unwilling

207
00:11:52,900 --> 00:11:54,580
to get along with your peers.

208
00:11:55,260 --> 00:11:57,700
How come you want to go to school suddenly?

209
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:01,180
Actually, I don’t mean to go to school either.

210
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:05,540
I just don’t want to stay at home.

211
00:12:07,060 --> 00:12:08,060
When I come to age,

212
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:10,380
they will betroth me to a man

213
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:12,500
and I still stay at home,

214
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:15,340
just at another home.

215
00:12:19,060 --> 00:12:19,540
Brother.

216
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:22,180
I want to go out and see the world.

217
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:25,780
But other than going to school,

218
00:12:26,900 --> 00:12:28,180
I have no other good reason

219
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,340
to go out.

220
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,900
Chacha’er.

221
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:42,260
You grow up.

222
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:46,420
OK.

223
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:50,260
I agree.

224
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:52,540
You can go to school.

225
00:12:54,020 --> 00:12:54,900
Really?

226
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,580
Don’t deceive me.

227
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:00,260
Brother.

228
00:13:01,500 --> 00:13:03,420
When will we go to school?

229
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:07,900
Do you want to leave me so much?

230
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,380
No.

231
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,500
I don’t want to leave you at all.

232
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,860
Are you still angry with me?

233
00:13:32,860 --> 00:13:33,860
The servants were here,

234
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:35,260
and I didn’t say it.

235
00:13:35,460 --> 00:13:36,140
You’d better

236
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,180
cut off your relationship with those performers.

237
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,620
How come you play around

238
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,620
with them?

239
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,900
That’s not a good business.

240
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,700
I am not playing around.

241
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:49,340
I take it as my career seriously.

242
00:13:49,940 --> 00:13:51,900
You know my major was liberal arts in college.

243
00:13:52,060 --> 00:13:53,420
I ever wrote scripts

244
00:13:53,660 --> 00:13:54,900
and played in dramas.

245
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,380
I like it.

246
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,580
Moreover, Peking opera is brilliant.

247
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:01,660
Shang Xirui is a rare talent.

248
00:14:01,940 --> 00:14:03,380
It’s worth my efforts.

249
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:04,740
Save it.

250
00:14:05,700 --> 00:14:07,300
Singing and acting

251
00:14:07,300 --> 00:14:08,900
are just for fun.

252
00:14:09,140 --> 00:14:10,700
You take it as your career?

253
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:12,620
You’re kidding me.

254
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:15,140
Stop making up lies.

255
00:14:15,620 --> 00:14:17,300
You think I'm a fool?

256
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:18,980
Chunxing.

257
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:20,100
Chunxing.

258
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:21,020
Make the bed.

259
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:23,860
Mr. Cheng will sleep in the study tonight.

260
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:24,540
Go out.

261
00:14:24,540 --> 00:14:25,380
I didn't deceive you.

262
00:14:25,380 --> 00:14:25,820
Go out.

263
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:27,180
-I mean it.
-Get out of my sight. Go.

264
00:14:32,460 --> 00:14:33,780
What’s wrong with her these days?

265
00:14:34,300 --> 00:14:35,780
I was rejected twice.

266
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:54,740
Isn’t it La Yuehong from Shuiyun Theater?

267
00:14:56,860 --> 00:14:58,220
What are you doing?

268
00:14:59,060 --> 00:14:59,860
Freeze.

269
00:15:01,140 --> 00:15:02,460
-What?
-Where are you heading?

270
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:06,580
Get away.

271
00:15:10,220 --> 00:15:13,460
The most important in our circle is hierarchy.

272
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:15,340
I am your senior.

273
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:19,100
You ignore me

274
00:15:19,100 --> 00:15:20,500
and disrespect me.

275
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:25,140
Since you bastard

276
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,460
have no manners,

277
00:15:28,180 --> 00:15:30,300
I will teach you a lesson

278
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:31,620
for your parents.

279
00:15:34,060 --> 00:15:34,900
Bros.

280
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:36,260
Catch him.

281
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:36,780
OK. OK.

282
00:15:36,940 --> 00:15:37,620
What are you doing?

283
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:39,060
Behave yourself.

284
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:51,700
You bastard.

285
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:57,340
Behave yourself.

286
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:04,140
Shuiyun Theater is full of

287
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:06,700
girls and toy boys.

288
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:09,380
All the toy boys are mean.

289
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:11,420
I dislike them.

290
00:16:11,580 --> 00:16:12,220
Buh.

291
00:16:12,660 --> 00:16:16,100
All the men of Spring Theater are bastards.

292
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:17,620
You talked back, huh?

293
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:18,700
You talked back?

294
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:19,860
Did you?

295
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:26,420
I’m here

296
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:28,100
to forward Chen Renxiang’s words

297
00:16:28,780 --> 00:16:30,700
to Shang Xirui.

298
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,100
Now that I meet you,

299
00:16:33,540 --> 00:16:35,300
I won’t bother to go there.

300
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:38,180
Jiang Dengbao.

301
00:16:39,100 --> 00:16:39,820
Bring me a pen.

302
00:16:40,020 --> 00:16:40,940
Wait a second, sir.

303
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:51,540
Sir. The pen.

304
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:52,980
Sir.

305
00:16:53,340 --> 00:16:54,460
I forgot to bring paper.

306
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:00,740
No paper is needed.

307
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:07,220
Is it Shuiyun Theater?

308
00:17:07,540 --> 00:17:08,140
Yes. Yes.

309
00:17:08,140 --> 00:17:09,500
What's the matter?

310
00:17:10,579 --> 00:17:12,380
I sell steamed buns at the North Street.

311
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,740
Is there a boy

312
00:17:13,740 --> 00:17:15,220
named La Yuehong here?

313
00:17:15,460 --> 00:17:17,900
He often eats vermicelli buns in my shop.

314
00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:18,700
I’m sorry.

315
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:20,300
La Yuehong.

316
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:21,900
Pay the bill.

317
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:23,460
Creditor comes for payment.

318
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:24,460
Don’t you feel ashamed?

319
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:25,940
La Yuehong went to buy strings.

320
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:26,940
No. No.

321
00:17:26,940 --> 00:17:28,300
He doesn’t owe me money.

322
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:29,860
That kid is being stripped naked

323
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:31,940
and tied to a pole on the street.

324
00:17:32,220 --> 00:17:32,860
It is freezing.

325
00:17:32,860 --> 00:17:34,300
What if he got sick?

326
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:35,460
Go and have a look quickly.

327
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:36,660
I gotta go.

328
00:17:36,900 --> 00:17:38,420
Buns are still being steamed on the steamer.

329
00:17:38,420 --> 00:17:38,740
Leader.

330
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:39,540
What to do, leader?

331
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:40,260
Alright.

332
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:41,420
Stop practicing.

333
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:42,620
All the men, come with me.

334
00:17:42,620 --> 00:17:43,540
Take weapons.

335
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,660
Let's go.

336
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:48,340
Don’t do anything if they don't fight first.

337
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:50,860
If they fight first, beat them to death.

338
00:17:51,380 --> 00:17:52,100
Go.

339
00:17:52,100 --> 00:17:52,780
You stay at home.

340
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:53,580
Why?

341
00:17:53,580 --> 00:17:55,220
You’re a spoiled young master. Don’t come.

342
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,300
I am a man as well.

343
00:17:56,300 --> 00:17:57,340
Mr. Du. Mr. Du.

344
00:17:57,340 --> 00:17:58,180
Mr. Du.

345
00:17:58,820 --> 00:17:59,700
Be careful.

346
00:18:02,820 --> 00:18:04,380
Who is he? It’s freezing.

347
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:10,940
Make way. Make way.

348
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:11,460
Where?

349
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:12,380
Make way. Make way.

350
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:15,380
Hurry.

351
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:16,180
Hurry. Hurry.

352
00:18:19,900 --> 00:18:21,180
There are words on your back.

353
00:18:21,180 --> 00:18:22,060
What words?

354
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:23,540
See you at the arena

355
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:24,540
on December ninth.

356
00:18:24,860 --> 00:18:25,380
Leader.

357
00:18:25,860 --> 00:18:27,460
It was done by Jiang Dengbao and his men.

358
00:18:27,780 --> 00:18:29,140
He meant to disgrace you.

359
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,260
I didn’t offend him.

360
00:18:31,260 --> 00:18:32,820
I didn’t.

361
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:57,180
♫ Wind and moon ♫

362
00:18:57,700 --> 00:18:59,060
Sir. Sir.

363
00:18:59,860 --> 00:19:01,620
Shang Xirui is coming with his men.

364
00:19:04,140 --> 00:19:04,940
It isn’t

365
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:07,060
his place anymore.

366
00:19:07,580 --> 00:19:08,860
How dare he run wild here?

367
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:09,620
Sir.

368
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:12,620
Even he wasn’t afraid of Commander Cao's gun.

369
00:19:12,620 --> 00:19:14,460
How can we deal with him?

370
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:17,220
Sir. How about we hide?

371
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:19,380
Shall we?

372
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:20,340
Yes.

373
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,620
Sir, this way.

374
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:28,140
Freeze.

375
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:29,980
What are you doing?

376
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:30,620
Sit down. Sit down.

377
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:31,380
None of your business.

378
00:19:34,940 --> 00:19:35,940
Mr. Shang.

379
00:19:36,220 --> 00:19:37,740
Isn’t it inappropriate

380
00:19:37,980 --> 00:19:39,020
to break into the backstage?

381
00:19:41,940 --> 00:19:42,860
Stay out of it.

382
00:19:43,740 --> 00:19:45,820
We meet a big shot, huh?

383
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:46,980
What?

384
00:19:47,740 --> 00:19:49,220
You ask for trouble?

385
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:50,340
La Yuehong.

386
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:52,140
Did he have you stripped?

387
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:53,820
Yes, leader.

388
00:19:54,020 --> 00:19:55,540
Did you beat him or curse him?

389
00:19:55,540 --> 00:19:57,300
You slept with his wife or dug his ancestral tomb?

390
00:19:57,300 --> 00:19:58,500
What are you talking about, bastard?

391
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,460
I did nothing.

392
00:19:59,780 --> 00:20:01,020
I tried to hide away when I saw him.

393
00:20:01,020 --> 00:20:02,380
I didn’t offend him at all.

394
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:04,100
So, he is asking for trouble.

395
00:20:13,780 --> 00:20:15,060
Please stop it.

396
00:20:15,620 --> 00:20:16,820
Please.

397
00:20:16,820 --> 00:20:18,100
Don’t beat me. Alright?

398
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:18,900
Stop it.

399
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:20,020
Mr. Shang.

400
00:20:21,300 --> 00:20:23,100
Don’t beat me. Stop.

401
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,780
Don’t. Don’t.

402
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:29,340
Go.

403
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:33,060
Shang Xirui.

404
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:35,020
This is Peking.

405
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:36,940
How dare you beat me?

406
00:20:36,940 --> 00:20:38,620
My father is the chairman of Opera Association.

407
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:39,580
I won’t let you off.

408
00:20:39,580 --> 00:20:40,580
Don’t do this.

409
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:41,820
Mr. Shang.

410
00:20:42,020 --> 00:20:43,380
Please speak your mind.

411
00:20:44,020 --> 00:20:44,820
Mr. Shang.

412
00:20:45,220 --> 00:20:45,980
Don't do this.

413
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:48,300
They are all prominent figures.

414
00:20:48,300 --> 00:20:49,540
People are watching.

415
00:20:49,540 --> 00:20:50,540
It isn’t proper.

416
00:20:50,940 --> 00:20:52,100
Dengbao offended you.

417
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,380
I apologize to you.

418
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:54,700
It has nothing to do with you.

419
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:57,020
I’m not here to ruin your business.

420
00:20:57,540 --> 00:20:59,620
Jiang Dengbao disgraced me.

421
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:02,140
If I don’t fight back,

422
00:21:02,620 --> 00:21:04,940
Shuiyun Theater will lose foothold in the circle.

423
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:05,820
Dasheng.

424
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:07,300
Bring me a pen.

425
00:21:07,300 --> 00:21:08,140
Please don’t.

426
00:21:08,620 --> 00:21:09,220
Hurry. Hurry.

427
00:21:09,220 --> 00:21:09,980
Don’t move.

428
00:21:10,260 --> 00:21:11,220
Sir. Sir.

429
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:13,100
Leader. Here.

430
00:21:13,100 --> 00:21:14,580
Let me help you write it.

431
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,460
Step aside.

432
00:21:17,460 --> 00:21:18,020
Come on.

433
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:19,220
Hold him for me.

434
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:21,940
Shang Xirui.

435
00:21:22,620 --> 00:21:23,740
What are you doing?

436
00:21:24,780 --> 00:21:25,980
Don’t you dare!

437
00:21:27,940 --> 00:21:29,140
Do you dare to touch me?

438
00:21:32,060 --> 00:21:32,860
Turn him around.

439
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:34,860
I won’t let you off!

440
00:21:36,780 --> 00:21:37,740
Shang Xirui.

441
00:21:37,740 --> 00:21:39,380
I tell you!

442
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,300
Leader.

443
00:21:46,020 --> 00:21:47,620
I won’t let you off.

444
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:50,060
Don’t you dare.

445
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:52,100
I dare.

446
00:21:52,100 --> 00:21:52,620
Come.

447
00:21:52,620 --> 00:21:53,620
Plug his mouth.

448
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:55,220
I will tell my father.

449
00:21:55,220 --> 00:21:56,740
I won’t let you off!

450
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:58,100
Shut up.

451
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:19,300
Tie him up.

452
00:22:24,340 --> 00:22:25,100
Everyone.

453
00:22:25,740 --> 00:22:27,300
On December ninth,

454
00:22:27,460 --> 00:22:28,940
Shang Xirui of Shuiyun Theater...

455
00:22:28,940 --> 00:22:31,380
It seems leader wrote one stroke less.

456
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:32,580
Don't talk.

457
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:35,780
I’ll spar with him by my new opera Zhao Feiyan.

458
00:22:36,020 --> 00:22:38,060
By then, welcome to

459
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:39,620
watch our competition,

460
00:22:39,620 --> 00:22:41,700
and be our judge.

461
00:22:41,820 --> 00:22:44,500
OK. OK.

462
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,940
Thank you! Thank you!

463
00:22:46,300 --> 00:22:47,380
Thank you!

464
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:48,380
OK.

465
00:22:48,780 --> 00:22:49,980
Shang Xirui.

466
00:22:50,420 --> 00:22:52,060
I won’t let you off!

467
00:22:53,860 --> 00:22:54,540
Stop watching.

468
00:22:54,540 --> 00:22:55,260
Untie me.

469
00:22:55,500 --> 00:22:56,940
Get away.

470
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,220
Stop watching.

471
00:22:58,660 --> 00:23:01,060
I will tell my father that you beat me!

472
00:23:01,660 --> 00:23:02,820
Hurry. Let me untie you.

473
00:23:02,820 --> 00:23:03,540
Sir.

474
00:23:07,780 --> 00:23:08,620
Listen up.

475
00:23:08,620 --> 00:23:10,380
Luozi Ridge is right ahead.

476
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:12,020
There are bandits.

477
00:23:12,260 --> 00:23:13,380
Let’s hurry up

478
00:23:13,380 --> 00:23:14,540
and pass it through tonight.

479
00:23:14,620 --> 00:23:16,140
As long as we get in Peking safely,

480
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:18,020
Chairman Zheng will handsomely reward

481
00:23:18,020 --> 00:23:19,580
all of us.

482
00:23:19,580 --> 00:23:20,820
OK. OK.

483
00:23:20,820 --> 00:23:22,580
Who dares to rob Chairman Zheng's goods?

484
00:23:22,900 --> 00:23:24,060
Don't move! Freeze!

485
00:23:26,380 --> 00:23:30,020
Hand out your goods.

486
00:24:20,620 --> 00:24:21,340
Listen.

487
00:24:21,860 --> 00:24:23,580
He is completely bewitched.

488
00:24:28,820 --> 00:24:33,180
Shang Xirui will battle with you by a new opera.

489
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:34,380
Do you know it?

490
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:36,940
Yes.

491
00:24:37,620 --> 00:24:39,020
He told me in person.

492
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:41,020
What about you?

493
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:44,340
What will you perform?

494
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,820
Hu Sanniang.

495
00:24:46,460 --> 00:24:49,140
Hu Sanniang against his Zhao Feiyan?

496
00:24:49,780 --> 00:24:51,700
It's your trump card.

497
00:24:51,900 --> 00:24:52,860
Good idea.

498
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:57,140
But audiences in Peking are all familiar with it.

499
00:24:58,100 --> 00:24:59,700
Uncle, what do you think?

500
00:25:00,740 --> 00:25:02,540
You perform Yan Xijiao.

501
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:07,820
I’m not good at playing Yan Xijiao.

502
00:25:08,580 --> 00:25:09,700
Renxiang.

503
00:25:10,940 --> 00:25:14,780
Do you know Sage’s Footwork of Jiang family?

504
00:25:19,420 --> 00:25:20,700
Are you a fool?

505
00:25:22,420 --> 00:25:24,620
Father will teach you Sage’s Footwork.

506
00:25:25,860 --> 00:25:27,260
That is the exclusive skill

507
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:29,540
of Jiang family and never be taught to outsiders.

508
00:25:30,260 --> 00:25:33,340
If you apply it on Yan Xijian,

509
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:37,980
it will be a big blast.

510
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:42,500
Her Highness watched that show,

511
00:25:42,780 --> 00:25:45,380
so she gave father a Royal Jacket delightedly.

512
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:47,740
It should be practiced from childhood.

513
00:25:48,620 --> 00:25:51,980
It’s kind of late for you to practice.

514
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:56,540
But it’s enough to satisfy

515
00:25:57,700 --> 00:25:59,180
the ordinary audiences.

516
00:26:04,540 --> 00:26:06,020
Thanks for your kindness, uncle.

517
00:26:06,180 --> 00:26:07,020
I will

518
00:26:07,780 --> 00:26:08,900
live up to your expectation

519
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:11,460
and earn you honor.

520
00:26:25,620 --> 00:26:27,180
It’s in the newspaper.

521
00:26:27,860 --> 00:26:31,780
Spring Theater’s opera is already determined.

522
00:26:32,180 --> 00:26:36,100
Chen Renxiang will perform Yan Xijiao.

523
00:26:37,220 --> 00:26:40,220
Why does he perform Yan Xijiao for competition?

524
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:41,940
Why?

525
00:26:42,300 --> 00:26:44,380
He wants to win.

526
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,300
Let me tell you.

527
00:26:47,620 --> 00:26:48,980
There is

528
00:26:49,340 --> 00:26:52,220
Sage's Footwork of Jiang family in Yan Xijiao.

529
00:26:52,780 --> 00:26:54,660
That old man uses the trump card

530
00:26:54,780 --> 00:26:56,780
of this family this time.

531
00:26:56,780 --> 00:26:57,540
What about you?

532
00:27:00,180 --> 00:27:02,740
How will you perform Zhao Feiyan?

533
00:27:05,940 --> 00:27:07,380
What do you mean?

534
00:27:07,540 --> 00:27:09,300
Have you decided it?

535
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:10,860
All the people in Peking

536
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,460
know you will perform Zhao Feiyan.

537
00:27:13,060 --> 00:27:14,180
You cannot even

538
00:27:14,180 --> 00:27:15,420
change your opera.

539
00:27:18,500 --> 00:27:20,420
Zhao Feiyan is ridiculous.

540
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:22,620
She seduced the emperor,

541
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:24,460
and also danced for him.

542
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:26,020
She made the trouble for me.

543
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:32,340
Are you blaming Zhao Feiyan?

544
00:27:32,340 --> 00:27:33,220
And you.

545
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:36,020
Your script is about that a maid becomes a queen.

546
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:37,860
You can write about anyone.

547
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:39,300
Why not you write about Wei Zifu?

548
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:40,460
Wei Zifu is good

549
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:41,580
and simple.

550
00:27:41,580 --> 00:27:44,380
I just need to stand on the stage

551
00:27:44,380 --> 00:27:46,100
and show the feather.

552
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:47,460
Can you be reasonable?

553
00:27:49,340 --> 00:27:51,300
I’m worried for you and my hair nearly goes gray.

554
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:52,340
But it seems

555
00:27:52,620 --> 00:27:54,340
you are not concerned.

556
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:55,980
You’re nagging.

557
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,420
You are scaring yourself.

558
00:27:57,420 --> 00:27:58,460
It’s a piece of cake.

559
00:27:58,460 --> 00:27:59,900
Let me show you right now.

560
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:01,020
Look.

561
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:23,180
Stop.

562
00:28:25,620 --> 00:28:27,060
I saw this.

563
00:28:28,380 --> 00:28:29,660
Isn’t it

564
00:28:29,860 --> 00:28:30,940
the Reunion?

565
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:33,980
Mr. Shang.

566
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:35,700
I am not frightening you.

567
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:37,540
Your footwork

568
00:28:37,980 --> 00:28:39,980
is no match of Sage’s Footwork

569
00:28:40,620 --> 00:28:42,220
at all.

570
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:44,140
What do you want to watch?

571
00:28:45,780 --> 00:28:47,100
Me?

572
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:50,540
You know Yang Yuhuan

573
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:52,300
and Zhao Feiyan.

574
00:28:53,100 --> 00:28:55,700
How is Zhao Feiyan like?

575
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:58,740
She is slim

576
00:28:59,700 --> 00:29:00,940
and graceful,

577
00:29:02,020 --> 00:29:03,700
flying with the wind

578
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:06,380
like a fairy.

579
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:08,060
That is absolutely

580
00:29:08,540 --> 00:29:10,020
nonsense.

581
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:11,420
What is your attitude?

582
00:29:11,740 --> 00:29:13,180
We’re discussing about the opera.

583
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:15,060
Opera is performed by people.

584
00:29:15,220 --> 00:29:16,980
People have brains.

585
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:18,860
Don’t try to use the words in books

586
00:29:18,860 --> 00:29:20,060
on me.

587
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:21,380
Impressive.

588
00:29:21,380 --> 00:29:23,460
You’re talking about opera by imagination.

589
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:24,500
You... You...

590
00:29:27,180 --> 00:29:27,780
I can’t reason

591
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:28,900
with you.

592
00:29:29,100 --> 00:29:30,860
I’m going to get some fresh air.

593
00:29:36,300 --> 00:29:37,340
Think about it.

594
00:29:38,260 --> 00:29:39,140
Zhao Feiyan.

595
00:29:41,380 --> 00:29:42,180
Graceful.

596
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:52,580
I didn’t scold you

597
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:53,700
in front of the leader.

598
00:29:53,900 --> 00:29:54,980
Don’t you know

599
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:56,420
your capability?

600
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:57,540
Sir.

601
00:29:57,540 --> 00:29:58,780
Please forgive him.

602
00:29:58,900 --> 00:29:59,740
Stay out of it.

603
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:02,060
Leader said I was better than you.

604
00:30:03,860 --> 00:30:05,620
Why should I give the role to you?

605
00:30:05,620 --> 00:30:07,100
Because I am your senior.

606
00:30:07,100 --> 00:30:08,260
So what?

607
00:30:08,500 --> 00:30:09,860
I don’t agree, no matter who you are.

608
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:10,980
-You...
-Shut up.

609
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:18,980
I heard it all.

610
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:22,900
Rules are rules.

611
00:30:23,660 --> 00:30:24,980
It can’t be changed casually.

612
00:30:26,460 --> 00:30:28,140
No one will take away your role.

613
00:30:28,140 --> 00:30:29,420
Rest assured.

614
00:30:31,260 --> 00:30:32,140
Leader.

615
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:35,460
Do you really let him replace me on the stage?

616
00:30:36,300 --> 00:30:37,900
Yes, I mean it.

617
00:30:39,780 --> 00:30:40,780
Fine.

618
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:42,980
You are unselfish.

619
00:30:43,460 --> 00:30:45,100
I’ve been through thick and thin for years

620
00:30:45,300 --> 00:30:47,060
in Shuiyun Theater.

621
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:50,940
You abandon me just for the contract?

622
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,820
Since we came to Peking,

623
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,660
you haven’t practiced your voice.

624
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:57,700
It’s an opportunity

625
00:30:57,980 --> 00:30:59,780
for these kids to experience on the stage.

626
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,700
You may take the time

627
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,980
to practice more.

628
00:31:03,220 --> 00:31:04,500
Isn’t it good?

629
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:07,580
Yes.

630
00:31:08,300 --> 00:31:09,180
It's good.

631
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,740
It is good indeed.

632
00:31:14,700 --> 00:31:16,500
We’re having meal. Where are you going?

633
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:18,100
No meal here for me anymore.

634
00:31:23,980 --> 00:31:24,900
Hi, Mr. Niu.

635
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:27,100
Don’t dissuade me.

636
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:28,620
I’ve decided to compete,

637
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:29,820
lest they say

638
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:31,380
I am spineless

639
00:31:31,380 --> 00:31:32,740
and afraid of Spring Theater.

640
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:34,300
Mr. Shang.

641
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:35,020
I know

642
00:31:35,020 --> 00:31:36,180
you fear no one.

643
00:31:36,780 --> 00:31:37,860
But Mr. Jiang

644
00:31:37,860 --> 00:31:39,460
is your grand master.

645
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:41,300
Whoever he is, I don’t admit it.

646
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:42,700
Right.

647
00:31:43,180 --> 00:31:47,020
I've never seen such a bully.

648
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:48,940
Young Master.

649
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:51,380
Please don’t put oil on fire.

650
00:31:53,100 --> 00:31:53,980
Mr. Shang.

651
00:31:54,420 --> 00:31:56,860
It’s a big deal to stop performing for one year.

652
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:59,140
Have you discussed it with Mr. Cheng?

653
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:01,060
No. It isn’t necessary.

654
00:32:02,580 --> 00:32:03,580
What is this about?

655
00:32:03,580 --> 00:32:04,620
Come on.

656
00:32:04,620 --> 00:32:05,900
Drink with me.

657
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:08,620
Look at him.

658
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:11,460
He isn’t in the mood.

659
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:19,300
What’s wrong?

660
00:32:20,060 --> 00:32:21,060
He has no idea of

661
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:23,500
how to perform Zhao Feiyan.

662
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:25,220
Neither of us can help him.

663
00:32:25,460 --> 00:32:26,740
Just drink with me.

664
00:32:26,740 --> 00:32:28,340
Come on. Drink.

665
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:29,300
Drink.

666
00:32:29,620 --> 00:32:30,500
Come on. Cheers.

667
00:32:30,500 --> 00:32:31,980
I know

668
00:32:32,300 --> 00:32:33,700
his temper very well.

669
00:32:33,700 --> 00:32:34,500
I come here

670
00:32:34,660 --> 00:32:35,460
in vain.

671
00:32:59,660 --> 00:33:02,020
Everyone encounters obstacles.

672
00:33:02,380 --> 00:33:03,540
Different people

673
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:05,260
have different ways to deal with them.

674
00:33:06,540 --> 00:33:07,780
I remember

675
00:33:08,260 --> 00:33:09,820
Mr. Ning used to

676
00:33:09,820 --> 00:33:11,820
go to the temple

677
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:13,740
when he was in bad mood.

678
00:33:14,100 --> 00:33:15,100
He stayed there all the afternoon,

679
00:33:15,380 --> 00:33:17,020
listening to chants and drinking tea.

680
00:33:17,020 --> 00:33:19,260
All the worries were forgotten,

681
00:33:20,220 --> 00:33:22,140
and the mood got better instantly.

682
00:33:23,340 --> 00:33:24,980
Bodhisattva.

683
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:28,220
I’ve been worried for days.

684
00:33:28,820 --> 00:33:30,780
I have no idea at all.

685
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:35,060
How do you think should I perform Zhao Feiyan?

686
00:33:36,620 --> 00:33:37,900
Please tell me

687
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:40,540
and give me a hint.

688
00:33:41,980 --> 00:33:43,740
If I get an idea,

689
00:33:44,380 --> 00:33:46,660
I’ll bring you goodies.

690
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:52,860
(Godmother Godmother)

691
00:33:52,860 --> 00:33:54,580
(Swing, godmother)

692
00:33:55,100 --> 00:33:56,740
Answer me, kid.

693
00:34:00,460 --> 00:34:01,540
Who is it?

694
00:34:01,900 --> 00:34:03,740
Sing Two Wives and One Husband in the temple.

695
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:05,580
Shameless.

696
00:34:27,139 --> 00:34:27,860
Mr. Shang.

697
00:34:28,260 --> 00:34:29,260
Someone came with a bird just now.

698
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,780
He gave me this and left.

699
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:31,540
It was for you.

700
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:32,980
Thanks.

701
00:34:45,139 --> 00:34:48,100
(Heavenly Fairy Salvation Sutra)

702
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:52,900
Sir,

703
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:53,900
Give me a hand.

704
00:34:53,900 --> 00:34:54,699
Hold it.

705
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:30,100
The flower is worth thousands of gold.

706
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:34,900
Give it to my dear friend.

707
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:40,020
Mr. Ning.

708
00:35:40,260 --> 00:35:41,260
Your bird

709
00:35:41,260 --> 00:35:42,580
does sing pleasantly.

710
00:35:44,180 --> 00:35:44,940
Right.

711
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:47,420
Did you give advice to Mr. Shang?

712
00:35:48,860 --> 00:35:51,140
I just gave him a painting.

713
00:35:51,700 --> 00:35:52,260
Gave him

714
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:53,380
a painting?

715
00:35:56,220 --> 00:35:58,820
Given Shang’s comprehension

716
00:35:59,620 --> 00:36:00,460
and talent,

717
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:05,100
if he can get over this obstacle,

718
00:36:06,020 --> 00:36:10,700
he may become an opera master.

719
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:12,260
But...

720
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:13,900
A painting?

721
00:36:16,100 --> 00:36:16,740
Are you leaving?

722
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:17,700
Take care.

723
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:18,620
Good day.

724
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:19,340
Sir.

725
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,460
Bye.

726
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:21,220
Good day.

727
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,500
I want a pot of Wine, sir.

728
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:23,700
Sure. Wait a second.

729
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:25,700
Waiter. Serve wine.

730
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:27,380
When the former leader died,

731
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:29,460
Shang Xirui was still a little kid.

732
00:36:29,460 --> 00:36:30,620
He knew nothing.

733
00:36:30,620 --> 00:36:31,900
We helped him

734
00:36:31,900 --> 00:36:34,020
with the business of Shuiyun Theater.

735
00:36:34,420 --> 00:36:35,620
But now

736
00:36:36,180 --> 00:36:37,260
he is fully fledged

737
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:38,700
and turns his back on us.

738
00:36:39,220 --> 00:36:40,540
Shang Xirui

739
00:36:40,940 --> 00:36:42,620
is ungrateful.

740
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:43,820
I can’t agree more.

741
00:36:44,220 --> 00:36:45,380
He used to be

742
00:36:45,380 --> 00:36:46,580
so kind to Jiang Mengping,

743
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:48,140
but now they ended up like this.

744
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:50,220
He is also cruel to us.

745
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:52,220
That brat La Yuehong

746
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:54,700
even doesn’t deserve to be our servant.

747
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:57,220
Shang Xirui favors him.

748
00:36:59,580 --> 00:37:00,900
He will regret sooner or later.

749
00:37:01,300 --> 00:37:02,700
Say no more.

750
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:04,540
Forget it. Let’s drink.

751
00:37:04,700 --> 00:37:05,780
Come on.

752
00:37:05,780 --> 00:37:06,620
Drink. Drink.

753
00:37:06,620 --> 00:37:07,740
Drink. Drink.

754
00:37:15,900 --> 00:37:18,420
What are you doing secretly?

755
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:20,460
Do you bring the wine?

756
00:37:20,460 --> 00:37:21,020
Sir.

757
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,660
I saw the men from Shuiyun Theater.

758
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,780
Darn it.

759
00:37:29,980 --> 00:37:31,460
How come I meet

760
00:37:31,460 --> 00:37:33,660
these bastards here?

761
00:37:33,660 --> 00:37:34,220
No.

762
00:37:34,220 --> 00:37:35,460
Sir. Listen to me.

763
00:37:38,380 --> 00:37:39,100
Are you sure?

764
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:39,980
Yes.

765
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:47,260
It’s at the midnight.

766
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,780
What is leader doing on the roof?

767
00:37:48,980 --> 00:37:49,460
Right.

768
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,500
It’s dangerous.

769
00:37:52,140 --> 00:37:54,100
-What’s wrong with him?
-Right.

770
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,140
It’s dangerous.

771
00:38:00,620 --> 00:38:01,660
Xiao Lai.

772
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:02,980
What’s wrong with the leader?

773
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,340
Right. What’s going on?

774
00:38:04,580 --> 00:38:06,460
He is insane.

775
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,340
He went to roof once he came back from the temple.

776
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:11,220
He could fall down and break bones.

777
00:38:12,420 --> 00:38:14,380
I’m worried.

778
00:38:14,660 --> 00:38:16,220
He has been practicing since childhood.

779
00:38:16,220 --> 00:38:17,980
He can even walk on chopsticks.

780
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:25,700
Leader's skills are good enough.

781
00:38:26,340 --> 00:38:28,340
Why does he have to learn Fairy Dance thing?

782
00:38:29,100 --> 00:38:30,380
He is meditating.

783
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:32,300
He must be concentrated

784
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,580
and forget everything

785
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:36,620
so that his skills can reach the peak.

786
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:40,380
To be a super star,

787
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,700
it is necessary.

788
00:38:42,980 --> 00:38:45,820
Or else, how can he achieve the top level?

789
00:38:47,340 --> 00:38:48,940
Back then Ning Jiulang

790
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:51,540
suffered a great disaster

791
00:38:52,100 --> 00:38:54,700
and then fully awakened.

792
00:38:55,140 --> 00:38:56,500
I wonder if Xirui

793
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,500
is lucky enough to do so.

794
00:38:58,500 --> 00:38:59,700
Now that it's a disaster,

795
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:00,700
how can he be lucky?

796
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:01,820
Right.

797
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:03,900
Leader. Leader.

798
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:12,460
Though it’s far away,

799
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,700
the dream is there.

800
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:13,300
How is it?

801
00:41:17,100 --> 00:41:18,660
Footwork is good enough,

802
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:23,660
but something is still not perfect.

803
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:24,740
Be patient.

804
00:41:25,100 --> 00:41:26,700
It’s boring to show

805
00:41:26,700 --> 00:41:27,420
all of the fun.

806
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:28,540
You don’t show it,

807
00:41:29,180 --> 00:41:30,540
but at least you should tell me.

808
00:41:30,820 --> 00:41:31,700
I...

809
00:41:32,020 --> 00:41:33,340
I want to dance on a drum

810
00:41:33,780 --> 00:41:34,980
as I play feathers.

811
00:41:35,500 --> 00:41:37,100
Chen Renxiang has one move,

812
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:38,220
I have a set of moves.

813
00:41:44,260 --> 00:41:45,420
Brilliant.

814
00:41:47,500 --> 00:41:48,980
That is what I want.

815
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,780
You are a genius.

816
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:54,740
You are absolutely a genius.

817
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:56,220
Genius.

818
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,940
No. No.

819
00:41:58,700 --> 00:42:00,180
I will write another opera for you right now.

820
00:42:01,260 --> 00:42:02,460
I will write another opera for you.

821
00:42:10,300 --> 00:42:11,940
Young Master thinks it’s good.

822
00:42:13,700 --> 00:42:15,540
What will Mr. Cheng say when he watches it?

823
00:42:19,220 --> 00:42:20,020
Xiao Lai.

824
00:42:20,580 --> 00:42:21,500
Is the meal ready?

825
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,620
Prepare more meat.

826
00:42:23,420 --> 00:42:24,580
Yes. It’s ready.

827
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:26,260
I’ve been waiting for you.

828
00:42:26,260 --> 00:42:27,180
Wait a minute.

829
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:36,260
Where did you go last night?

830
00:42:36,860 --> 00:42:38,100
What are you doing here?

831
00:42:49,220 --> 00:42:50,260
What’s wrong?

832
00:42:54,340 --> 00:42:57,380
The new rules on the contract

833
00:42:57,380 --> 00:42:58,540
are all true?

834
00:42:58,660 --> 00:42:59,620
Yes.

835
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:00,500
What’s wrong?

836
00:43:04,380 --> 00:43:05,140
Father.

837
00:43:06,980 --> 00:43:07,740
Father.

838
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,620
Great news, father.

839
00:43:11,580 --> 00:43:13,380
You scared me.

840
00:43:15,860 --> 00:43:16,780
Shoot.

841
00:43:21,820 --> 00:43:22,660
(Contract)

842
00:43:22,660 --> 00:43:22,940
I got those masters of Shuiyun Theater
(Contract)

843
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:24,780
I got those masters of Shuiyun Theater

844
00:43:25,020 --> 00:43:26,620
to us.

845
00:43:27,580 --> 00:43:29,540
I also get some information

846
00:43:29,540 --> 00:43:31,620
about his new opera.
